  Other-Modules:     Control.Concurrent.SCC.Streams, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Types, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Coercions,
                     Control.Concurrent.SCC.Combinators, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Primitives,
